"T:Rebirth of Desire for Knowledge":

We're detecting even more powerful
[Loser] readings in Omega!
We expect this battle to be extremely
dangerous, so we're only sending in ARKS
who've proven they're the best of the best!
――――――――――――――――――――
Max Damage Cap: 999999
Failure: Fail objective, time limit expires"
